  "detailed_description": "In this electrifying game, you will collect cards and evolve your characters to become powerful enough to eliminate entire hordes of zombies.<br><br><strong>Zombie Survivors</strong> is an action and survival roguelite where you have to fight and defeat thousands of zombies and other monsters that appear to devour you.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect gold and gems to buy improvements.<br></li><li>Unlock Pets with unique abilities to help you defeat hordes of enemies.<br></li><li>Unlock new characters.<br></li><li>Collect cards and evolve them to improve their attributes.</li></ul><br>Various types of attacks, skills, and pets to fight against the hungry enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/b5641c5241dcba5089867001f55cc325.poster.avif?t=1751467604\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/b5641c5241dcba5089867001f55cc325.webm?t=1751467604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/b5641c5241dcba5089867001f55cc325.mp4?t=1751467604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect chests and spin the roulette for a chance to win great buffs in the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/a6e6237a10b44aaf6f1f3eb6399806e1.poster.avif?t=1751467604\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/a6e6237a10b44aaf6f1f3eb6399806e1.webm?t=1751467604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/a6e6237a10b44aaf6f1f3eb6399806e1.mp4?t=1751467604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Search for and collect cards left by bosses. Upgrading them with gems will give you significant and essential improvements for game progression.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/4a6f845729c97bef15699fee37b9f6bc.poster.avif?t=1751467604\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/4a6f845729c97bef15699fee37b9f6bc.webm?t=1751467604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/4a6f845729c97bef15699fee37b9f6bc.mp4?t=1751467604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect coins and buy new powerful pets with unique abilities that will help you in this great battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/cbe0345354f818ee18181ba09805c458.poster.avif?t=1751467604\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/cbe0345354f818ee18181ba09805c458.webm?t=1751467604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/cbe0345354f818ee18181ba09805c458.mp4?t=1751467604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "In this electrifying game, you will collect cards and evolve your characters to become powerful enough to eliminate entire hordes of zombies.<br><br><strong>Zombie Survivors</strong> is an action and survival roguelite where you have to fight and defeat thousands of zombies and other monsters that appear to devour you.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect gold and gems to buy improvements.<br></li><li>Unlock Pets with unique abilities to help you defeat hordes of enemies.<br></li><li>Unlock new characters.<br></li><li>Collect cards and evolve them to improve their attributes.</li></ul><br>Various types of attacks, skills, and pets to fight against the hungry enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/b5641c5241dcba5089867001f55cc325.poster.avif?t=1751467604\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/b5641c5241dcba5089867001f55cc325.webm?t=1751467604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/b5641c5241dcba5089867001f55cc325.mp4?t=1751467604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect chests and spin the roulette for a chance to win great buffs in the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/a6e6237a10b44aaf6f1f3eb6399806e1.poster.avif?t=1751467604\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/a6e6237a10b44aaf6f1f3eb6399806e1.webm?t=1751467604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113890/extras/a6e6237a10b44aaf6f1f3eb6399806e1.mp4?t=175146